What is the output of this program?

```java
class recursion
{
    int func (int n)
    {
        int result;
        if (n == 1)
            return 1;
        result = func (n - 1);
        return result;
    }
}

class Output
{
    public static void main(String args[])
    {
        recursion obj = new recursion();
        System.out.print(obj.func(5));
    }
}
```

What is the output of this program?

```java
class recursion
{
    int fact(int n)
    {
        int result;
        if (n == 1)
            return 1;
        result = fact(n - 1) * n;
        return result;
    }
}

class Output
{
    public static void main(String args[])
    {
        recursion obj = new recursion();
        System.out.print(obj.fact(5));
    }
}
```

